parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause the vehicle to become difficult to control, increasing the risk of accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: The power steering system fails
making the vehicle hard to steer
warning lights illuminate on the dashboard
and the vehicle may lose speed or become unstable.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering system can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: The steering system fails
making the vehicle difficult to control
the steering wheel becomes hard to turn
and warning lights may illuminate on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Delays in recall repairs can leave vehicles on the road with safety defects, increasing the risk of accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: Vehicle owners receive recall notifications
but parts are not available
or dealerships are unable to perform the repairs in a timely manner.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electronic stability control system can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: The electronic stability control system fails
warning lights illuminate on the dashboard
and the vehicle may lose traction or become unstable.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to stall, lose power, or become stuck in gear, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission slips or hesitates
the vehicle stalls or loses power
the transmission makes unusual noises
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear
the transmission warning light is illuminated.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the clutch pedal does not return to its normal position
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the drive shaft can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents.
symptoms: The drive shaft breaks or becomes loose
the vehicle loses control
the vehicle makes unusual noises.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle's systems to malfunction, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The infotainment screen glitches or freezes
the radio turns off or on unexpectedly
the vehicle's lights malfunction
the vehicle's systems shut down.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The stalling of the engine can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine stalls while driving
the vehicle loses power
the check engine warning light is illuminated.
